Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.85,Secondary,NTP,0,0,0,,「どうした マコト」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.73,Secondary,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.16,Secondary,NTP,0,0,0,,
